In partnership with the Women’s Sports Foundation, @crackerjackofficial_ is launching the I Am Cracker Jill Contest to highlight the inspiring accomplishments of women and girls in sports. This initiative will award 9 female athletes aged 15-24 the prize of $5,000 to fuel their sports dreams, with one lucky winner becoming the new face of Cracker Jill. Applications are open now, full rules at link in my bio. #IAmCrackerJill

#AD A day in my life, off day edition. I love @crackerjackofficial_ because it’s delicious, but also because of the commitment they make to uplifting women and girls in sports. This year, the I Am Cracker Jill Contest will award 9 winners (female athletes between the ages of 15 and 24) $5,000 to fuel their sports dreams, as well as making one lucky winner the new face of Cracker Jill! This cause is so close to my heart and I hope you’ll apply :) Full rules linked in my bio! #IAmCrackerJill
